{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/react/react-hooks-사용-시-주의할-점들/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Memory !== Record","author":"Ayaan","siteUrl":"https://alpaca92.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"Alpaca92/alpaca92.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"ayaan92"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bf5af23a-705e-5fc9-93a4-711c26e7e52c","excerpt":"오늘은 여태 react hooks을 사용하면서 겪었던 경험들을 바탕으로 사용시 주의할 점에 대해 정리해보고자 한다 (따라서 불편함을 겪거나 궁금한 점이 있을 때마다 업데이트가 될 것 같다) 정리하기에 앞서 리엑트가 렌더링되는 조건을 가볍게 되짚어보면 가 변경되었을 때 가 변경되었을 때 가 리렌더링 될 때 useState() useState를 const로 사용하는 이유 우리가 를 사용할 때에는 일반적으로 다음과 같이 사용한다 state는 분명 변경되는데 어째서 state를 변경 불가능한 const…","html":"<p>오늘은 여태 react hooks을 사용하면서 겪었던 경험들을 바탕으로 사용시 주의할 점에 대해 정리해보고자 한다</p>\n<p>(따라서 불편함을 겪거나 궁금한 점이 있을 때마다 업데이트가 될 것 같다)</p>\n<p>정리하기에 앞서 리엑트가 렌더링되는 조건을 가볍게 되짚어보면</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">State</code>가 변경되었을 때</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Props</code>가 변경되었을 때</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Parent component</code>가 리렌더링 될 때</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"usestate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usestate\" aria-label=\"usestate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useState()</h1>\n<h2 id=\"usestate를-const로-사용하는-이유\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usestate%EB%A5%BC-const%EB%A1%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0\" aria-label=\"usestate를 const로 사용하는 이유 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useState를 const로 사용하는 이유</h2>\n<p>우리가 <code class=\"language-text\">useState</code>를 사용할 때에는 일반적으로 다음과 같이 사용한다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useState <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// do something..</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>state는 분명 변경되는데 어째서 state를 변경 불가능한 const로 선언하였을까?</p>\n<p>이를 알기 위해서는 useState가 동작하는 방식에 대해 알 필요가 있다</p>\n<h2 id=\"setstatesetter는-비동기로-작동한다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#setstatesetter%EB%8A%94-%EB%B9%84%EB%8F%99%EA%B8%B0%EB%A1%9C-%EC%9E%91%EB%8F%99%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"setstatesetter는 비동기로 작동한다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>setState(setter)는 비동기로 작동한다</h2>\n<p>setState를 하고나서 console.log를 통해 변경된 state 값을 확인해주는 경우는 흔하다</p>\n<p>하지만 가끔 setState를 한 후 console.log를 찍어도 값이 변하지 않는 경우가 있었는데</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">incrementState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 예상 출력: 4</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 실제 출력: 0</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이런 상황이 일어나는 이유는 바로 <code class=\"language-text\">setState</code>가 비동기로 동작하기 때문이다</p>\n<p><strong><em>그렇다면 왜 <code class=\"language-text\">setState</code>는 비동기로 동작하는 걸까?</em></strong></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">useState</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">Object.is()</code>를 사용해 state의 변화를 감지하고 변화가 있다면 해당 컴포넌트부터 자식컴포넌트까지 <code class=\"language-text\">render()</code>를 실행해 렌더링을 한다</p>\n<p>그렇다면 빠르게 만번, 십만번 이상 state가 변한다면 어떻게 될까?</p>\n<p>당연히 성능적인 측면에서 이슈가 발생할 것이기에 리엑트는 <strong>16ms 동안 변경된 상태 값들을 모아서 한번에 리렌더링</strong>하는 <code class=\"language-text\">Batch Update</code>방식을 사용한다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">incrementState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 예상 출력: 4</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 실제 출력: 0</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>따라서 위 코드는 <code class=\"language-text\">incrementState</code>가 끝난 후에 state의 update가 반영된다<br />(콜스택이 다 비워진 후 콜백 큐에 있는 비동기 처리가 이벤트 루프에 의해 콜스택으로 들어오기 때문에)</p>\n<p>비동기에 대해 잘 모르겠다면 <a href=\"https://alpaca92.github.io/dev/%EC%9E%90%EB%B0%94%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC-(1)/\">이글</a>을 읽고오길 권장한다</p>\n<h1 id=\"useeffect\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useeffect\" aria-label=\"useeffect permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useEffect()</h1>\n<h2 id=\"deps에-state가-아닌-일반-변수를-넣으면-어떻게-될까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deps%EC%97%90-state%EA%B0%80-%EC%95%84%EB%8B%8C-%EC%9D%BC%EB%B0%98-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%EB%A5%BC-%EB%84%A3%EC%9C%BC%EB%A9%B4-%EC%96%B4%EB%96%BB%EA%B2%8C-%EB%90%A0%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"deps에 state가 아닌 일반 변수를 넣으면 어떻게 될까 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>deps에 state가 아닌 일반 변수를 넣으면 어떻게 될까?</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">deps</code>에 일반적인 형태의 변수는 넣어도 리엑트는 이를 업데이트 하지 않는다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> normalCounter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'effect: counter updated'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>normalCounter<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>normalCounter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>normalCounter<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button\n        onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">++</span>normalCounter<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n          console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">normalCounter: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>normalCounter<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        click me\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'render: i am rendered'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같은 코드에서 초기 렌더링 시에는 콘솔에서는</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">render: i am rendered\neffect: counter updated</code></pre></div>\n<p>순으로 출력되며, <code class=\"language-text\">click me</code> 버튼을 세 번 클릭하면</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;1회>\nnormalCounter: 1\n\n&lt;2회>\nnormalCounter: 2\n\n&lt;3회>\nnormalCounter: 3</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">normalCounter</code>의 값은 증가하지만 리렌더링은 발생하지 않는다</p>\n<p>그렇다면 <code class=\"language-text\">state</code>를 넣어 비교해보도록 하자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">init</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'state: init function was fired'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setCounter<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> normalCounter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'effect: counter updated'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>counter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>normalCounter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>normalCounter<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button\n        onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token function\">setCounter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>counter <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">++</span>normalCounter<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n          console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">counter: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>counter<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">, normalCounter: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>normalCounter<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        click me\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'render: i am rendered'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>초기 렌더링 시에는</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">state: init function was fired\nrender: i am rendered\neffect: counter updated</code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">state initialization</code> > <code class=\"language-text\">rendering</code> > <code class=\"language-text\">useEffect</code>순으로 실행되며, 똑같이 <code class=\"language-text\">click me</code> 버튼을 세 번 클릭하면</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;1회>\ncounter: 0, normalCounter: 1\nstate: init function was fired\nrender: i am rendered\neffect: counter updated\n\n&lt;2회>\ncounter: 1, normalCounter: 1\nstate: init function was fired\nrender: i am rendered\neffect: counter updated\n\n&lt;3회>\ncounter: 2, normalCounter: 1\nstate: init function was fired\nrender: i am rendered\neffect: counter updated</code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같다</p>\n<p>여기서 <code class=\"language-text\">counter</code>가 1, 2, 3이 아닌 이유는 <code class=\"language-text\">setCounter</code>와 동일한 scope에 있기 때문에 아직 리렌더링이 일어나기 전이라 이전 값을 출력하기 때문에 0, 1, 2로 출력된다</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">normalCounter</code>의 경우는 버튼이 클릭될 때마다 <code class=\"language-text\">setCounter</code>에 의해 <code class=\"language-text\">state</code>가 변경되어 리렌더링되어 다시 선언되어 항상 0이 되기 때문에 버튼을 몇번 누르냐와 관계없이 항상 1이 출력된다</p>\n<h2 id=\"dependency의-비교-알고리즘-이해하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dependency%EC%9D%98-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"dependency의 비교 알고리즘 이해하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>dependency의 비교 알고리즘 이해하기</h2>\n<p>리엑트는 항상 객체와 배열을 그들의 reference로 비교한다</p>\n<p>즉, 두 객체(혹은 배열)이 완벽하게 동일하더라도 reference가 다르면 다르다고 판단해 useEffect를 다시 실행시킨다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> userDetails <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  username<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Kim'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> userDetails2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  username<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Kim'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>userDetails <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> userDetails2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// false</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>따라서 이런 경우 개발자의 의도와는 다르게 동작할 수 있다</p>\n<p>이를 해결하기 위해서는 <strong>좀 더 명확한 dependency를 사용</strong>하면 된다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> userDetails <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  username<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Kim'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> userDetails2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  username<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Kim'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>userDetails<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>someKey <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> userDetails2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>someKey<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// true</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>useEffect를 사용한다면 다음과 같을 것이다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">UserProfile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> userDetails <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setError<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>userDetails<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>username<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Do something…!</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>userDetails<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>username<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>하지만 이 방법은 매우 작은 정보만을 담고있는 객체(혹은 배열)에서만 가능한 방법이다</p>\n<p>이를 위해 우리는 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Memoization\">메모이제이션(memoization)</a>을 해서 비교하는 것이 바람직하다는 것을 알 수 있다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">UserProfile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> userDetails <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setError<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> username<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> email<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> address <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> userDetails<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> user <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useMemo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">createUser</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> username<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> email<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> address <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    username<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    email<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    address<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>username<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Do something…!</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같이 작성하면 createUser 함수는 username, email, address가 변경될 때에만 실행되어 새로운 유저객체를 생성한다</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>결론은 dependency array에 넣는 data type이 <strong>primitive type(Boolean, Number, String, Null, Undefined)</strong>라면 예상대로 동작하지만 <strong>object type(Object, Function, Array)</strong>을 넣는 경우에는 <strong>reference compare</strong>를 하는데 매 렌더링마다 새로운 메모리주소에 할당되므로 항상 콜백이 실행된다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>🍪 추가로 <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react/blob/ddd1faa1972b614dfbfae205f2aa4a6c0b39a759/packages/react-reconciler/src/ReactFiberHooks.new.js#L296\">dependency array비교 코드</a>를 보면 useEffect뿐만 아니라 다른 훅들에서도 사용되고 있다 짐작할 수 있다</p>\n<h2 id=\"references\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#references\" aria-label=\"references permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>*references</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://dudghsx.tistory.com/18\">hooks에서 useState가 const로 선언되는 이유</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hewonjeong.github.io/deep-dive-how-do-react-hooks-really-work-ko/\">[번역] 심층 분석: React Hook은 실제로 어떻게 동작할까?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hae-ong.tistory.com/97\">[React] setState를 했는데 console.log엔 새로운 값이 반영이 안되는 이유</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dev.to/ms_yogii/useeffect-dependency-array-and-object-comparison-45el\">UseEffect dependency array and object comparison!</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://sgwanlee.medium.com/useeffect%EC%9D%98-dependency-array-ebd15f35403a\">React useEffect 의 dependency array</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://velog.io/@ckvelog/dependency-array-shallow-equal\">의존성 배열은 shallow compare (equal), deep equal 중 어떤 것을 할까?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/suyeonme/react-lets-deep-dive-into-deps-array-of-useeffect-13ab96468db7\">React: Let’s deep dive into deps array of useEffect</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://yceffort.kr/2022/04/deep-dive-in-react-rendering#%EB%A6%AC%EC%97%91%ED%8A%B8-%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81-%EA%B7%9C%EC%B9%99\">리액트의 렌더링은 어떻게 일어나는가?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://felixgerschau.com/react-rerender-components/\">When does React re-render components?</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"React Hooks 사용 시 주의할 점들","date":"October 04, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/react/react-hooks-사용-시-주의할-점들/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/react/react-lifecycle-with-hooks/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React lifecycle vs hooks"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/dev/resolution-and-units/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"해상도와 디스플레이 단위(px, dp, sp, pt)"}}}}}